00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.740
&gt;&gt; NOTEFOLDS: Note Folds dot com presents
Puppy Dog Note Fold.

00:00:10.740 --> 00:00:11.769
[pause]

00:00:11.769 --> 00:00:18.270
Start with one notebook piece of paper. Fold
in half vertically.

00:00:18.270 --> 00:00:21.060
[pause]

00:00:21.060 --> 00:00:23.850
Unfold.

00:00:23.850 --> 00:00:34.140
Fold the top down horizontally.

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:36.550
[pause]

00:00:36.550 --> 00:00:44.460
Now fold the upper left corner down to the
center line, making sure the upper left edge

00:00:44.460 --> 00:00:47.470
is aligned with the fold made in step one.

00:00:47.470 --> 00:00:48.470
[pause]

00:00:48.470 --> 00:00:57.200
Repeat on the right side.

00:00:57.200 --> 00:01:00.160
[pause]

00:01:00.160 --> 00:01:03.670
Now unfold everything.

00:01:03.670 --> 00:01:09.700
[pause]

00:01:09.700 --> 00:01:13.420
Fold diagonally on the fold you just made.

00:01:13.420 --> 00:01:15.409
[pause]

00:01:15.409 --> 00:01:16.509
Repeat on the other side.

00:01:16.509 --> 00:01:23.229
[pause]

00:01:23.229 --> 00:01:26.439
Orient the paper horizontally.

00:01:26.439 --> 00:01:30.689
Push in on the sides. You're trying to collapse
the inner edge.

00:01:30.689 --> 00:01:33.130
[pause]

00:01:33.130 --> 00:01:35.579
Flatten.

00:01:35.579 --> 00:01:38.029
[pause]

00:01:38.029 --> 00:01:43.130
Turn over with the point down and the holes
on the top.

00:01:43.130 --> 00:01:44.130
[pause]

00:01:44.130 --> 00:01:48.429
Fold the left corner down to the center line,
aligning the upper left edge with the center.

00:01:48.429 --> 00:01:53.489
[pause]

00:01:53.489 --> 00:01:56.270
Repeat this on the right side.

00:01:56.270 --> 00:01:58.819
These will be the puppy dog's eyes.

00:01:58.819 --> 00:02:00.889
[pause]

00:02:00.889 --> 00:02:03.799
Turn the page over.

00:02:03.799 --> 00:02:11.849
Fold the upper edge down as far as it will
go on the left.

00:02:11.849 --> 00:02:12.849
[pause]

00:02:12.849 --> 00:02:17.860
Repeat this on the right.

00:02:17.860 --> 00:02:20.320
[pause]

00:02:20.320 --> 00:02:25.459
Turn the page over.

00:02:25.459 --> 00:02:26.689
[pause]

00:02:26.689 --> 00:02:30.500
Fold the right flap down to create the ear.

00:02:30.500 --> 00:02:32.730
[pause]

00:02:32.730 --> 00:02:35.400
Repeat this on the left.

00:02:35.400 --> 00:02:37.319
[pause]

00:02:37.319 --> 00:02:43.859
Fold the bottom point up just a bit to make
the nose.

00:02:43.859 --> 00:02:46.239
[pause]

00:02:46.239 --> 00:02:50.090
You've just completed the Puppy Dog Note Fold.

00:02:50.090 --> 00:02:51.090
[pause]

00:02:51.090 --> 00:02:59.060
